Utility scripts to merge small inputs:

    list.pl  - lists the available unspent inputs from the wallet
    xlist.pl - lists the available unspent inputs from keys not in the wallet
    pick.pl  - shows the optimal set of inputs to reach the target value
    send.pl  - constructs a transaction and sends it

Dependencies:

    bitcoind
    perl >= 5.10
    perl modules listed in cpanfile
